data.description: Charming 1-story home conveniently located near Lackland Airforce Base and Dove Creek shopping centers off 1604 and 90 West. This cozy residence features a welcoming open floor plan, offering ample natural light throughout. The well-appointed kitchen boasts modern appliances and a breakfast bar, perfect for entertaining. The comfortable living area is ideal for relaxation and has direct access to a lovely backyard, great for outdoor activities. With its convenient location and cozy atmosphere, this home is perfect for those seeking convenience and comfort in the vibrant Far west, Lackland area.
